    <item>
      <title>英国就业市场出现降温迹象，令京东方有所缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/uk-unemployment-rate-rises-unexpectedly-as-pay-growth-eases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于工资增长放缓，英国失业率自 7 月以来首次上升，进一步证明劳动力市场正在降温，并缓解了英国央行担忧的部分通胀压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/uk-unemployment-rate-rises-unexpectedly-as-pay-growth-eases</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 07:09:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国要求一些银行限制对离岸地方政府融资平台债券的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/china-asks-some-banks-to-limit-backing-lgfvs-offshore-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国监管机构要求中国一些银行限制使用偿还支持机制，该机制支持地方政府融资平台发行离岸债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/china-asks-some-banks-to-limit-backing-lgfvs-offshore-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 07:09:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市开始见证各个行业的牛市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/china-stocks-begin-witnessing-bull-markets-in-a-gamut-of-sectors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国一些新旧经济领域的牛市已经开始，这表明投资者看到了习近平主席提振经济和市场的措施带来的当前估值的上升空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/china-stocks-begin-witnessing-bull-markets-in-a-gamut-of-sectors</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 07:06:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
