      <title>据路透社报道，中国李宁公司考虑将运动服装公司私有化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/china-s-li-ning-mulls-taking-sportswear-company-private-reuters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社援引未具名人士的消息报道，中国体操运动员出身的企业家李宁正在考虑将其同名运动服装品牌从香港股市私有化。股价飙升 20%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/china-s-li-ning-mulls-taking-sportswear-company-private-reuters</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 06:12:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
